  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "The linter says it cannot find the \"Templates\" (uppercase) directory. We should make that \"templates\" since file systems can be case sensitive.\n\n```\nhelm [master]$ bin/helm create mychart\nCreating mychart\nmychart [master*]$ ls\nChart.yaml  charts      templates   values.yaml\nhelm [master*]$ bin/helm lint mychart\nLint OK\nhelm [master*]$ rm -rf mychart/templates/\nhelm [master*]$ bin/helm lint mychart\n[WARNING] Templates directory not found\nhelm [master*]$\n\nhelm [master*]$ cd mychart/\nmychart [master*]$ ls\nChart.yaml  charts      values.yaml\nmychart [master*]$ mkdir Templates\nmychart [master*]$ cd ..\nhelm [master*]$ bin/helm lint mychart\nLint OK\n```\n\ncc/ @migmartri @technosophos \n",
